name: 2 Miniature Fruit Tarts for Fashion Royalty Barbie Doll 1/6 Scale Playscale Dessert Kawaii
description:
This listing is for 2 adorable fruit tarts for your Barbie sized dolls like Fashion Royalty, Monster High and Poppy Parker. 

Handmade from polymer clay and fruit slices. Each one has kiwi, strawberry, banana, papaya, orange, lemon and blueberries and then the tops are glazed with a clear varnish. Each one measures almost 5/8" inch wide, approximately 3/8" inch tall. Email me if you'd like a larger quantity.

Great for Barbie and Fashion Royalty dolls and all dollhouse kitchen displays or dioramas.

**Pastry platters not included. Other treats available in other listings.

name: 2 Miniature Hostess Cupcakes for Fashion Royalty Barbie Doll 1/6 Scale Playscale Dessert Kawaii
description:
This listing is for 2 tiny, adorable little chocolate Hostess cupcakes for your Barbie sized dolls like Fashion Royalty, Monster High and Poppy Parker.

Made from polymer clay and hand painted with a chocolate color. The white swirls are hand made from air dried clay and then the tops are glazed with a clear varnish. Each one measures 0.5" inch wide, 3/8" inch tall. Email me if you'd like a larger quantity.

Great for Barbie and Fashion Royalty dolls and all dollhouse kitchen displays or dioramas.

**Pastry platters not included. Other treats available in other listings.
